      "protocol": "1. Seed cells in 96-well plate (5000 cells/well)\n2. Allow 24h attachment\n3. Add drug treatments per protocol schedule\n4. At each timepoint: add CellTiter-Glo reagent (1:1 v/v)\n5. Incubate 10 min RT, read luminescence\n6. Normalize to Day 0 vehicle control"
